Analytics for Communications-Business

Create CRM Analytics for Communications-Business App

Required editions and user permissions: Developer edition and Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions. Permission sets needed: CRM Analytics Plus Admin and CRM for Comms Admin.

To create an app from the template:

1. Click Create in CRM Analytics Studio.
2. Select App, then Create App from Template.
3. Choose the CRM Analytics for Communications-Business app tile.
4. Review the app preview page and click Continue.
5. Name your app and click Create.
